	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Your touch afflicts your victim with a magical disease.</em></p><p><strong>[[/save constitution]]{Constitution Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 8d10 poison]] damage and gains the &amp;reference[diseased] condition. While diseased in this way:</p><ul><li><p>The target is &amp;reference[poisoned] and has &amp;reference[disadvantage] on saving throws.</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul>",
